=Description=

"an interdisciplinary course that focuses on new technologies applied to the textile industry, ranging broadly from fashion to wearables markets. This 6-month educational program is offered in select laboratories across the world. If you are interested in this journey at the intersection of textiles, digital fabrication and biology please join us by registering for the 2019-2020 Fabricademy class! STARTING DATE:  September 24th, 2019"


=Status=

Fifth edition in 2021:

* program that brings together emerging technologies and innovation around textiles, wearables and biodesign. Fabricademy will open up new disciplines, capabilities and opportunities in your fab lab! 

